    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. CFD-predicted NIH agrees with in-vitro measurements within 8.3% mean relative error, satisfying the 15% acceptance criterion. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use.",
